'''Jane Doe''' (November 24, 1972 - October 11, 2022) was a globetrotter who lived in eight countries over eight years. 

==Early life==
Jan was born in a town or city named "Anonymous," named so because its exact location is ambiguous. Her mother is Gabrielle Doe (born 1948), a now-retired police officer, and her father was an unknown hoodlum that hardly had a role in Jane's life, if at all.

